title: Openstreetmap Geofabrik, Netherlands- Flevoland Roads, Netherlands- Northern Flevoland, 2008
name: Openstreetmap Geofabrik, Netherlands- Flevoland Roads, Netherlands- Northern Flevoland, 2008
description: This Dataset is part of 35 datasets downloaded from the openstreetmap, Geofabrik website and includes information and locations of roads throughout northern Flevoland in the Netherlands. The dataset includes Road names and type. Type of road includes information on whether the road is a primary, residential or secondary road, etc. It also includes foot and bicycle paths. Because the dataset for the entire country was too big, it was divided into provinces and then those were divided into sections. There are a total of 35 sections.
